subject: Vuelta a Espana (Bicycle Race)
Bicycles and Bicycling
Cycling, Road
lead_paragraph: Warren Barguil of France won the mountainous 16th stage of the Vuelta a España, timing his final sprint up the steep Aramon Formigal peak.
